00:18:34,400 --> 00:18:35,650
Yes.

373
00:18:37,850 --> 00:18:42,700
So you are also involved in this project.

374
00:18:42,700 --> 00:18:44,510
It is tough working together, right?

375
00:18:44,510 --> 00:18:45,810
I'll tell my boss to remove me from this project.

376
00:18:45,810 --> 00:18:47,090
Why?

377
00:18:48,670 --> 00:18:52,500
Don't you think you're being pretentious?

378
00:18:53,720 --> 00:18:58,060
That kind of thing, on the contrary, pisses me off.

379
00:18:59,130 --> 00:19:01,880
- I'm sorry.
