380
00:19:01,880 --> 00:19:04,180
If you apologize...

381
00:19:08,750 --> 00:19:10,530
This is annoying.

382
00:19:11,490 --> 00:19:13,470
Right now, I'm the only one who knows the truth

383
00:19:13,470 --> 00:19:16,350
besides the two of them.

384
00:19:16,350 --> 00:19:19,740
Only I can help her out of this situation.

385
00:19:25,970 --> 00:19:27,840
Hey, Narushima-san.

386
00:19:27,840 --> 00:19:28,990
Yes?

387
00:19:28,990 --> 00:19:30,740
Can I have a moment with you?

388
00:19:30,740 --> 00:19:31,950
What's the matter?

389
00:19:32,630 --> 00:19:34,380
Only I...

390
00:19:35,460 --> 00:19:37,200
Maruya-san...

391
00:19:37,200 --> 00:19:38,980
There's only me.

392
00:19:42,710 --> 00:19:43,790
Well...

393
00:19:44,760 --> 00:19:46,080
What is it?

394
00:19:47,170 --> 00:19:48,820
If you don't mind...

395
00:19:52,780 --> 00:19:54,580
Take this.

396
00:19:54,580 --> 00:19:57,130
Why did I give him a can of café au lait?

397
00:19:57,130 --> 00:19:58,890
What should I do?

398
00:19:58,890 --> 00:20:00,770
What should I do?

399
00:20:01,680 --> 00:20:03,150
I have some preparation work to do.

400
00:20:03,150 --> 00:20:04,970
I will head to the meeting room first.

401
00:20:04,970 --> 00:20:07,670
Has the meeting started yet?

402
00:20:07,670 --> 00:20:09,130
Am I in time for it?

403
00:20:12,980 --> 00:20:14,190
What happened?

404
00:20:15,940 --> 00:20:18,440
Did Sanada leak some information again?

405
00:20:18,440 --> 00:20:19,770
What? Are you saying it?

406
00:20:19,770 --> 00:20:21,670
So that rumor...

407
00:20:21,670 --> 00:20:24,160
It seems everyone heard it.

408
00:20:24,160 --> 00:20:26,490
Sanada, it's all right for me to say it, right?

409
00:20:27,560 --> 00:20:30,620
She was in the product development department

410
00:20:30,620 --> 00:20:32,840
before she was assigned to sales.

411
00:20:32,840 --> 00:20:36,560
At that time, there was a leak of information.

412
00:20:36,560 --> 00:20:38,460
She told everyone about

413
00:20:38,460 --> 00:20:40,720
my liver function test result.

414
00:20:40,720 --> 00:20:41,800
What?

415
00:20:43,490 --> 00:20:46,370
Well, I went way over the standard values in my physical exam.

416
00:20:46,370 --> 00:20:48,700
They said I drank too much beer.

417
00:20:48,700 --> 00:20:50,510
Is that what you mean by information leakage?

418
00:20:50,510 --> 00:20:51,860
Yes, that's right.

419
00:20:51,860 --> 00:20:54,960
I thought that was what you meant!

420
00:20:54,960 --> 00:20:58,450
Sanada, whose health checkup figures did you leak this time?

421
00:20:58,450 --> 00:21:01,770
After this, we're all going to taste the croquettes, right?

422
00:21:01,770 --> 00:21:02,391
Yes!

423
00:21:02,391 --> 00:21:05,510
I'll forget the health checkup figures today.

424
00:21:06,370 --> 00:21:08,880
It's time for the meeting. Let's go.

425
00:21:08,880 --> 00:21:11,460
- Yes.
- Narushima, let's go.

426
00:21:11,460 --> 00:21:12,720
Yes.

427
00:21:28,650 --> 00:21:30,390
Thank you for your hard work.

428
00:21:34,800 --> 00:21:37,160
In the end,

429
00:21:37,160 --> 00:21:39,530
I couldn't do anything for her.

